- Goodbye.

441
00:26:58,880 --> 00:26:59,720
Alright, goodbye.

442
00:27:11,519 --> 00:27:12,200
Miss Tan.

443
00:27:13,039 --> 00:27:14,359
Why didn't Ye Haitang come today?

444
00:27:15,759 --> 00:27:17,079
She took a few sick days.

445
00:27:17,359 --> 00:27:17,960
Sick leave?

446
00:27:19,039 --> 00:27:19,720
What sick leave?

447
00:27:20,039 --> 00:27:20,960
Her dad requested it

448
00:27:21,039 --> 00:27:21,839
this morning.

449
00:27:22,119 --> 00:27:22,920
Her father?

450
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:27,519
Where are you going?

451
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:28,519
I'm taking leave, too.

452
00:27:29,279 --> 00:27:30,680
It's your first day back today.

453
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:31,400
Tang Yixun!

454
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:33,519
Ye Haitang!

455
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:38,720
Ye Yibo!

456
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:40,400
Ye Yibo!

457
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:42,680
Ye Yibo!

458
00:27:57,119 --> 00:27:57,720
Ye Yibo!

459
00:28:04,759 --> 00:28:05,559
What's your problem?

460
00:28:05,559 --> 00:28:06,440
Who? What's going on?

461
00:28:07,519 --> 00:28:08,119
Ye Yibo?

462
00:28:08,519 --> 00:28:09,200
Haven't seen him.

463
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,279
Was he here recently?

464
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:11,400
With unpaid debts

465
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:12,559
and new ones now,

466
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:14,240
how could he come?

467
00:28:14,559 --> 00:28:15,720
Three against one?

468
00:28:16,079 --> 00:28:16,839
This.

469
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:20,160
Hello.

470
00:28:21,039 --> 00:28:22,640
Is this the Fenghua Sugar Factory?

471
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,319
May I speak to Ye Yibo?

472
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,119
I... I am...

473
00:28:27,119 --> 00:28:28,200
I'm his relative.

474
00:28:28,519 --> 00:28:29,240
He's on leave?

475
00:28:31,039 --> 00:28:31,839
When?

476
00:28:32,799 --> 00:28:33,160
Okay.

477
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:33,960
Thank you.

478
00:28:39,519 --> 00:28:40,039
Sir.

479
00:28:47,582 --> 00:28:50,759
(Meiwan Police Station)

480
00:28:50,759 --> 00:28:51,680
Take it easy.

481
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:52,319
Speak slowly.

482
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,440
What are you to Ye Haitang?

483
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:55,559
Classmate.

484
00:28:56,119 --> 00:28:56,799
Classmate?

485
00:28:56,799 --> 00:28:57,079
Yeah.

486
00:28:57,279 --> 00:28:58,839
Does the school know

487
00:28:58,839 --> 00:28:59,559
she's missing?

488
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:01,160
Her dad asked for leave,

489
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:02,440
but he's suspicious.

490
00:29:02,839 --> 00:29:04,039
What's wrong with her father?

491
00:29:04,599 --> 00:29:05,680
Give this to Liu.

492
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:06,319
Got it.

493
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:10,920
You are the girl's classmate

494
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:12,440
from last time, right?

495
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:12,720
Yes.

496
00:29:13,319 --> 00:29:13,880
What's wrong?

497
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:16,440
He reported his classmate missing,

498
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:17,240
but

499
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:19,200
the parent already notified the school.

500
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,240
Same girl as before?

501
00:29:21,319 --> 00:29:21,680
Yes.

502
00:29:22,680 --> 00:29:24,240
Did her dad take her to the hospital?

503
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:28,559
They say she has delusions.

504
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,759
Treatable.

505
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,839
Many tell me to send her
to a psychiatric hospital.

506
00:29:38,599 --> 00:29:39,240
Mr. Chen!

507
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:40,920
Let me borrow your bike.

508
00:29:41,079 --> 00:29:41,880
Let me use it.

509
00:29:42,039 --> 00:29:42,759
Alright.

510
00:29:43,519 --> 00:29:44,359
Calm down.

511
00:29:45,319 --> 00:29:46,319
Return it tonight, Xun.

512
00:29:46,319 --> 00:29:46,880
Okay.

513
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:50,680
Make way.

514
00:30:20,176 --> 00:30:27,408
(Mental Rehabilitation Center)

515
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:31,799
Tang.

516
00:30:32,799 --> 00:30:34,160
Don't blame me for being harsh.

517
00:30:34,559 --> 00:30:35,519
It's for your own good.

518
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:36,880
They'll feed you.

519
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,039
Focus on getting better.

520
00:30:38,839 --> 00:30:40,319
Wait till I sell the house

521
00:30:40,559 --> 00:30:41,240
and win big.

522
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:42,160
I'll come back for you.

523
00:30:54,079 --> 00:30:54,680
Tang.

524
00:30:55,279 --> 00:30:56,119
We're here now.

525
00:30:56,240 --> 00:30:57,039
Go along.

526
00:30:57,720 --> 00:30:58,960
Let me untie you.

527
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,119
No more outbursts, okay?

528
00:31:00,119 --> 00:31:01,240
Work with the doctors.

529
00:31:02,880 --> 00:31:04,400
Stay still. Isn't this better?

530
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:10,559
I'm fine, really.

531
00:31:10,559 --> 00:31:11,359
My child is ill.

532
00:31:11,359 --> 00:31:12,319
Why hit me again?

533
00:31:12,519 --> 00:31:13,400
It's okay.

534
00:31:13,839 --> 00:31:15,160
My child is ill.

535
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,319
I'm here with you.

536
00:31:16,599 --> 00:31:17,920
It's alright.

537
00:31:18,119 --> 00:31:18,839
We're here.

538
00:31:18,839 --> 00:31:19,400
We're here.

539
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:20,559
We're at the hospital.

540
00:31:21,599 --> 00:31:22,240
Ye Haitang!

541
00:31:22,599 --> 00:31:23,559
Ye Yibo!

542
00:31:23,559 --> 00:31:24,359
We're here.

543
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,200
Ye Yibo!

544
00:31:40,359 --> 00:31:41,559
Raising your hand against me?

545
00:31:42,119 --> 00:31:42,960
Ye Yibo!

546
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:44,759
Ye Yibo!

547
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:46,480
You're an animal!

548
00:31:49,839 --> 00:31:50,960
You hit me?

549
00:31:52,759 --> 00:31:53,680
I'm her father!

550
00:31:54,319 --> 00:31:55,160
I make the rules!

551
00:31:55,319 --> 00:31:56,640
I'll do whatever I want!

552
00:31:56,799 --> 00:31:57,680
You can't stop me!

553
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,400
Ye Yibo!

554
00:32:02,319 --> 00:32:03,279
What did she do wrong?

555
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:04,759
Why treat her like this?

556
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:09,920
She tried to stab me!

557
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:10,799
She tried to kill me!

558
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,039
To stab me to death!

559
00:32:13,599 --> 00:32:14,519
Go ahead! Kill me!

560
00:32:18,279 --> 00:32:19,759
Come on, Ye Yibo!

561
00:32:21,519 --> 00:32:23,039
- Stop it!
- Stop!

562
00:32:23,039 --> 00:32:23,880
No more fighting!

563
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:24,839
He will die!

564
00:32:24,839 --> 00:32:25,640
Ye Yibo!

565
00:32:26,039 --> 00:32:26,839
He will die!

566
00:32:27,319 --> 00:32:27,960
Let go!

567
00:32:28,279 --> 00:32:29,480
Stop fighting!

568
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:30,160
Ye Yibo!

569
00:32:30,880 --> 00:32:31,839
You beast!

570
00:32:32,039 --> 00:32:33,720
Do it! Kill me!

571
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:34,640
Ye Yibo!

572
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,720
My own daughter tried to stab me!

573
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:38,799
She brought

574
00:32:38,799 --> 00:32:39,799
this punk to kill me!

575
00:32:39,960 --> 00:32:41,000
Come on! Kill me!

576
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:41,759
Don't you run!

577
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:42,960
Stay right there!

578
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:44,799
You beast!

579
00:32:45,839 --> 00:32:46,640
Ye Yibo!

580
00:32:46,880 --> 00:32:47,400
Stop!

581
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,200
Don't run away!

582
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:49,240
Get lost!

583
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:52,559
Ye Haitang.

584
00:33:04,039 --> 00:33:04,720
I'm sorry.

585
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:07,359
I'm sorry.

586
00:33:15,079 --> 00:33:15,839
I'm sorry.

587
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:26,279
I'm sorry.

588
00:33:31,839 --> 00:33:32,640
Let's go home.

589
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,599
Let's go home.

590
00:33:36,021 --> 00:33:41,392
♪This road is too long♪

591
00:33:43,734 --> 00:33:48,752
♪Must we be like this♪

